OL,3,CInvestigating the career of the
OL,4,Ceditor of the Scottish Farmer
OL,6,FWatch the full episode of Border Life.
OL,8,FKen Fletcher has retired as editor of
OL,9,Fthe Scottish Farmer. He is an award
OL,10,Fwinning journalist who worked on the
OL,11,Fpaper for 46 years.
OL,13,FHe travelled the globe to see how
OL,14,Fothers do things in the world of
OL,15,Ffarming. He covered major stories
OL,16,Fincluding foot and mouth.
OL,18,FHe has been helping out on farms
OL,19,Fsince he was a boy. At the age of 17
OL,20,Fhe got a job that would keep him
OL,21,Fclose to the land.
